              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </content>
      </section>
      <paragraph>
        <content>
          <p><span style="color:#000000"><b><i>I have read the Impact Assessment and I am satisfied that (a) it represents a fair and reasonable view of the expected costs, benefits and impact of the policy, and (b) that the benefits justify the costs.</i></b></span></p>
          <table uk:widths="2.95in 1.88in 0.59in 1.4in">
